metadata.name: Overtime
metadata.description:
Finding Frames is a collection born out of the artist's appreciation for the worlds that exist behind frames that disconnect two worlds while also connecting them. 

Artist: Saram Maqbool
Edition type: 1/1
Location: Poland

License: The primary NFT holder is free to use this NFT in advertising, displaying privately and in groups, including virtual galleries, documentaries, and essays by the holder of the NFT, as long as the creator 'Saram Maqbool' is credited. No rights to create commercial merchandise, commercial distribution, or derivative works are provided. Copyright remains with the creator, Saram Maqbool.
